Accessing FRED This function can pull time series from the FRED database: https://fred.stlouisfed.org

Source: R/get_econ_series.R
get_econ_series.Rd

Accessing FRED This function can pull time series from the FRED database: https://fred.stlouisfed.org

get_econ_series(series_id,
series_name = NULL,observation_start = NULL,
 observation_end = NULL)

Arguments

series_id

FRED times series ID, the unique id retrieved from fed database.
series_name

Choose a name for the series column in output. Default: series_id.
observation_start

Choose a name for the series column in output. Default: series_id.
observation_end

Date of last observation in "yyyy-mm-dd" format. Default: Last observation available.

Examples

get_econ_series("UNRATE", "unemploymentRate")
